public sealed interface Definition permits CustomIdJDAEntity<T>, Invokable, JDAEntity<T>, InteractionDefinition, ModalDefinition.TextInputDefinition, OptionDataDefinition, OptionDataDefinition.ConstraintDefinition, SlashCommandDefinition.CooldownDefinition, StringSelectMenuDefinition.MenuOptionDefinition
